					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7997185#post-4034501</guid>
				<title>Re: Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7997185/scp-4442#post-4034501</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 23 Oct 2018 18:25:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Matthew Baranyai</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3987412</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>If this is your first article ever, I'm looking forward to what you will do in the future. While I think this would be more fitting as a SCP-XXXX-J with some tweaking, I certainly enjoyed it a lot. However, you made it work as a regular article (what got me was the bit about the D-Class who ran over his girlfriend, and that was some <strong>really</strong> dark humor so that worked), so I don't think it was misclassified.</p> <p>You're clearly a talented writer, and I hope more people see this. God knows I couldn't write this well (I've been trying to write a successful article for nearly a year). Godspeed.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
